Visualize data

DimPlot(ATH_root, reduction = "umap", label = TRUE)

Find marker genes

ATH_root_marker <- FindAllMarkers(ATH_root, only.pos = TRUE, min.pct = 0.5, logfc.threshold = 0.5) %>% 
  group_by(cluster) %>% arrange(cluster, desc(avg_log2FC))
